10 REM SOUND DEMO FOR ORIC-1
20 REM DEMONSTRATES AY-3-8910 PSG
30 CLS
40 PRINT "  *** ORIC-1 SOUND DEMO ***"
50 PRINT
60 PRINT "  PLAYING ASCENDING SCALE..."
70 PRINT
80 REM PLAY ASCENDING TONES ON CHANNEL A
90 FOR I=1 TO 8
100 SOUND 1,500-I*50,15
110 FOR D=1 TO 500:NEXT D
120 NEXT I
130 PRINT "  PLAYING DESCENDING SCALE..."
140 FOR I=8 TO 1 STEP -1
150 SOUND 1,500-I*50,12
160 FOR D=1 TO 500:NEXT D
170 NEXT I
180 PRINT
190 PRINT "  PLAYING THREE CHANNELS..."
200 SOUND 1,200,10
210 SOUND 2,250,10
220 SOUND 3,300,10
230 FOR D=1 TO 2000:NEXT D
240 SOUND 1,0,0
250 SOUND 2,0,0
260 SOUND 3,0,0
270 PRINT
280 PRINT "  DONE! PRESS ANY KEY."
290 GET A$
300 END
